- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is a possible category as the paper deals with automatic linear orders, which are related to formal languages and automata theory. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with the isomorphism of linear orders, which is a topic in game theory.
